Chavez’s Medical Team Says He’s ‘Absolutely Satisfactory’

-- B y   J o s e   O r o z c o
-- 
2011-10-22T20:20:57Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-22/chavez-s-medical-team-says-he-s-absolutely-satisfactory-.html
Venezuelan President  Hugo Chavez ,
who has been treated for cancer, was diagnosed and treated on
time and his “current evolution is absolutely satisfactory with
an excellent prognosis,” according to a statement read by Dr.
Fidel Ramirez of the Military Hospital on state television.  Ramirez is part of Chavez’s medical team.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Jose Orozco in Caracas at 
 jorozco8@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
